br />\n「陳雲」係一個團體<br />\n而「陳云根」就係出嚟講野果個人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而個經營手法，就係果d 瑞士山區肺騙案，即係扮有個唔關事既路人行過「咦，咁抵？」於昰就左手 share 右手，然後右手又 share 左手，做到好似好多人 share，後來者懞下懞下，仲以為點解d 9up 咁勁，係咪自己真係唔夠聰明，睇唔明 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04e164182f7bb79afd210c3afa2a47347e3904fc","tid":38013,"uid":1893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T16:29:06.000Z","msg":"成件事合理晒<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/96bM5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F96bM5.gif&h=17bc13bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7f991708f4ad3c38aad9e0075551ae3cd4984148","tid":38013,"uid":46849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T16:29:33.000Z","msg":"其實係幾識玩 Facebook 既，以一個老人家黎講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0c1995d517fa21aa3b95d55f76b44b7b685d074","tid":38013,"uid":46849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T16:32:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成件事合理晒<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/96bM5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F96bM5.gif&h=17bc13bb&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n確實解釋左好多現象，亦好合理 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55b10365e8db8c60d63b69a10e36712472e5c30d","tid":38013,"uid":47663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T16:40:49.000Z","msg":"有朋友係陳雲fans, 不過睇唔明佢地講乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb59d93489c23c4b105453de124506140f7eb382","tid":38013,"uid":46849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T16:42:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有朋友係陳雲fans, 不過睇唔明佢地講乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>咁都做到 Fans？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5156e824a55d0d865b7186a39a1d2e004e4f039","tid":38013,"uid":650